<bibRefCitation author="Kenk" box="[507,799,740,766]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" refString="Kenk, V. C. &amp; Wilson, B. R. (1985) A new mussel (Bivalvia, Mytilidae) from hydrothermal vents in the Galapagos Rift zone. Malacologia, 26, 253 - 271." type="journal article" year="1985">
